## What's On Our List

These rows are known gaps between shipped CSS and the intended system direction. Close each gap in CSS, then delete its row.

| # | Token | Shipped now | Target | Why |
|---|-------|-------------|--------|-----|
| 1 | `success` / `warning` ladders | Base only | Full solid/outline set like accent | Solid success/warning buttons are not supported yet |

Until this lands, success and warning should stay as text, border, or icon treatment. Do not build solid success or warning surfaces with hand-rolled `emerald-*` or `amber-*`.
